{"tid":1434223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【危急】政府文宣搞左幾日，我地捱打緊呀！！！","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:30:36.000Z","uid":293406,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"83080c0d114ffb10555b23796c4908afe108abc4","tid":1434223,"uid":293406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"黑警4點例行記招＋政府5點跨部門記招搞左4日，全方位文宣轉移視線，我地而家被捱打呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n黑警完全唔介意記者追問佢地，你有你問，我有我鳩答，點解？<br />\n無論你記者問乜好，CCTVB只會播返黑警照住讀既維穩新聞稿，Q＆A完全唔會出現！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點拆：</span></span><br />\n黑警一出現，記者要輪流問佢地問題，唔好比任何機會佢地讀稿。黑警唔答唔緊要，不斷問，用晒佢地啲air time。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有咩後果：</span></span><br />\n1. 黑警可能會要求不斷問問題的記者離開。仲好，少一間電視台既 air time，其他記者接力<br />\n，最好趕晒所有記者走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 記招無辦法繼續舉行，宣佈取消。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 記者可以早點收工返屋企瞓覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府跨部門記招可用類似方法。<br />\n以至林鄭出黎見記者都一樣。唔好比佢講，一黎就問佢幾時回應5大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n希望記者朋友可以大家一起合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我地而家係全民對抗緊一個名副其實既黑幫極權政府，仲用佢定既方法幫佢做文宣，只有死路一條！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03461199265d7e15b54dbb1d1f84bd9992c328e7","tid":1434223,"uid":293406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a249e9a2aee7bc5730300d6cfef8b279986b9160","tid":1434223,"uid":293406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"21b3240c67dc8d73e5dbe0a64055ab801f31efd6","tid":1434223,"uid":293406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:56:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2aaa184933afe7aa3f5fb4844a7f0942be629d47","tid":1434223,"uid":293406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:56:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7d73f6e2d6d62eda3b0a81031065df69d546abb2","tid":1434223,"uid":293406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:57:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"88d472c14a9954b41571fa951fafb4b5f0e5d4f1","tid":1434223,"uid":293406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:30:06.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"4ae5db7dd6e546fdc618719f07bd72bd0cfe255e","tid":1434223,"uid":293406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"b3dde12f04b7b68f46ef14991cfa32bd72620fad","tid":1434223,"uid":293406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:30:36.000Z","msg":"再自推"}]}